{"tid":1668957,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我係大陸人，學緊廣東話，多謝你地包容","createTime":"2019-10-22T09:35:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T10:35:35.000Z","uid":287814,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5e22a281dd42ec76c85d0fbe6851748435550e31","tid":1668957,"uid":287814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T09:35:41.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇到呢個討論有小小驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1668164/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1668164/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n我都係大陸人，依家學緊廣東話，深知身在香港要尊重本土文化。香港同事朋友也都好照顧，習慣用普通話同我交談，在此多謝包容大陸同事的巴絲，多謝🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n但係我覺得，每個人語言能力唔同，我就比較慢啲，也比較shy，唔好意思開口講，不過依家準備多實踐練習<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真正熱愛香港的人，都會支持香港嘅普世價值。六月以後，我本人睇國旗同埋穿紅衣啲人，都會覺得唔舒服，見到講普通話啲人，都覺得似粉紅五毛咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過，以語言或外貌揣測政治立場，似有小小唔妥。公司仲有唔少深黃大陸同事，我也識好多不懂廣東話的大陸朋友，都希望為香港民主運動，奉獻小小力量。<br />\n<br />\n總之，多謝多謝多謝包容<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd44f2fb5dbf91b78de16bc4b84c7d260c82fd55","tid":1668957,"uid":100028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T09:41:39.000Z","msg":"Hi 你喺大陸邊度"},{"pid":"e24adbefc9d7f54fb4965d3179110d0421bdd572","tid":1668957,"uid":220000,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T09:42:27.000Z","msg":"Hi你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a7ae3b0bbc572ebf47d24ed3ad6d8bebf3dc93a","tid":1668957,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T09:42:52.000Z","msg":"歡迎加入"},{"pid":"c2dd1472436856209dbce18a17d746706009790b","tid":1668957,"uid":60594,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T09:43:02.000Z","msg":"Post大陸身分證 加連登名再講"},{"pid":